      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "ELITE GENERAL (6) held his own to the line last start and filled a minor placing, beaten only 2 lengths (17.38) behind CHAROS JOURNEY at this track. The form from his last run is stacking up nicely. Good form should continue. CHAROS JOURNEY (4) goes very well at the course with four wins and a placing from 10 starts. Below best last time at this track (17.34) in a Free For All, finishing a 4.5 lengths fourth. Looks suited here and can measure up. HONG KONG PHOOEY (1) raced close to the lead throughout before colliding in the run, finishing a 1.75 lengths third (22.85) in a Grade 4/5 at Mandurah. Harder here but will be in this for a long way. MACARONI MONELLI (2) is last start winner who looks one of the chances.",
